## Do's and Don'ts

### Do
- Use tokens from this file — never ad-hoc values
- Test color contrast (WCAG AA minimum)
- Include all interactive states (hover, focus, active, disabled)
- Design mobile-first, enhance for larger screens

### Don't
- Use Inter, Roboto, or Arial as the primary display font
- Use purple gradients on white backgrounds
- Nest cards inside cards
- Use bounce/elastic easing
- Ship components without error and loading states
- Use gray text on colored backgrounds without checking contrast

